    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3232010/extras/1c661e6d585ea45f534860787a3a67eb.avif?t=1730896361\" width=462 height=174 /></span></p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Face your fears, and hope emerges from the shadows.</strong></p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Thirty rooms, each hiding a new danger, where the wrong step can cost you everything. Three doors stand before you, but only one offers a way forward. Solve the puzzles, trust your instincts, and hope it’s enough to escape. One wrong choice, and you’ll be lost to the darkness. Listen carefully, watch closely &quot; your senses are your only guide. Thirty rooms. </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >One path to freedom. The question is... can you find it? Open the door. <br> <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3232010/extras/5d0fffe170dd5eaf2325b9f1581d0afc.poster.avif?t=1730896361\" width=544 height=306 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3232010/extras/5d0fffe170dd5eaf2325b9f1581d0afc.webm?t=1730896361\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3232010/extras/5d0fffe170dd5eaf2325b9f1581d0afc.mp4?t=1730896361\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br> <br>Notice: </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The pictures on the wall in the game are generated by AI.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The narrator voices in the game are AI-generated.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Average playtime: 60 - 120 minutes.</p>",
